title: The Miracle In The Mismatch (Tim Timberlake)
description: Don’t stop short of your miracle. In “The Miracle In The Mismatch,” Pastor Tim Timberlake of Celebration Church reveals that the seeds of your miracle are often sown in the soil of adversity.
dc:creator: Elevation Church
